| Notes                   = * It has been stated by the producer of the movie, Todd Casey, that this movie is intended to take place between ''[[Marvel's The Avengers]]'' and its sequel.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130304032713/https://www.marvel.com/news/story/20216/iron_man_hulk_unite_for_the_holidays_in_new_animated_film|title=Iron Man & Hulk Unite for the Holidays in New Animated Film|work=Marvel.com|date=February 28, 2013|accessdate=March 04, 2013|last=|first=}}</ref>
* The movie was initially slated for an April 23, 2013, release. It is currently unknown why the film was pushed back until early December of the same year.
* The movie reused some assets from [[Avengers Initiative (video game)]]. For example, the models of Abomination and Zzzax.
| Trivia                  = * A clip for a sequel of this movie, called ''Iron Man and Captain America: Heroes United'' has been revealed in Amazon.com.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/gp/mpd/permalink/m27O0JMRP2O6UT/ref=ent_fb_link|title=Amazon.com : Iron Man and Hulk Heroes United|date=December 4, 2013|accessdate=December 4, 2013}}</ref>
